						<summary>

						<p><hi rend="bold">Manmatha (1415 A.D.)</hi></p>						

						<p>Eulogises the achievements of the king in a chronological sequence com mencing with the cyclic year Pārthiva equivalent to Śaka 1327 and states that <hi rend="bold">Uttama-Nambi</hi> was the recipient of several honours such as the parasol etc., from king Dēvarāya.</p>						

						<p>The last verse refers to the consecration of the Garuḍa image by <hi rend="bold">Chakrarāja</hi> in <hi rend="bold">Manmatha, Jyēshṭha, Sunday, Rēvati</hi> which corresponds to <hi rend="bold">A.D. 1415, June 2, Sunday, [ba. 10, ·75], ·40.</hi></p>						

						</summary>
